    "Several providers make similar promises about the general LLMs they offer; other Gen AI solutions do not make any such promises.",
    "Some firms employ open-source models (e.g., Llama) in private clouds to address privacy concerns.",
    "Researchers should examine how Gen AI users balance increased privacy and IPR protection versus, for example, reduced costs to implement and deploy a Gen AI solution.",
    "We need scholarly attempts to probe the boundary conditions of when the benefits of privacy and IRP protections result in adequate returns on the investments needed to institute such protections.",
    "A key issue relates to bias: Gen AI can amplify the biases present in an LLM."
